object.customQuery:
select
	a.SystemId,
	a.ParentId,
	a.CMMContainer,
	a.Id,
	a.UpdateCount,
	a.UpdateUser,
	a.UpdateTimestamp,
	a.TemplateIdRef,
	a.TypeCd,
	a.SourceCd,
	a.StatusCd,
	a.ResultCd,
	a.RequestTypeCd,
	a.TransmittedDt,
	a.TransmittedTm,
	a.ReceivedDt,
	a.ReceivedTm,
	a.ProcessedDt,
	a.ProcessedTm,
	a.AddDt,
	a.AddTm,
	a.PartyId,
	a.RowId,
	a.StateSpecificCode,
	a.InspectionNumber,
	a.InspectionId
from
datareport a
inner join advrxxchangedbeans b 
	on a.Systemid = b.Systemid
	and a.CmmContainer = b.CmmContainer
	and b.CmmContainer = 'DataReport'
WHERE 
CONCAT(b.adddt, ' ', substr(b.addtm, 1, 8));
